## Key Columns Reference

```sql
-- stripe_sync.subscriptions key columns:
-- id              TEXT  — Stripe subscription ID (sub_...)
-- customer_id     TEXT  — Stripe customer ID (cus_...)
-- status          TEXT  — active | trialing | past_due | canceled | incomplete | unpaid
-- current_period_start  TIMESTAMPTZ
-- current_period_end    TIMESTAMPTZ
-- cancel_at_period_end  BOOLEAN
-- metadata        JSONB  — your custom metadata including user_id
-- attrs           JSONB  — full raw Stripe object

-- stripe_sync.customers key columns:
-- id              TEXT  — Stripe customer ID (cus_...)
-- email           TEXT
-- metadata        JSONB  — your custom metadata including user_id
```

